Buy a blutooth beacon
Program an app that detects bluetooth beacons' IDs
Make a loop to count the bluetooth beacons
If there are more than 10 bluetooth beacons
    Play an MP3 file to alert people to keep a distance between each other
If there are 10 or less bluetooth beacons
   Count again
If a problem occurs
    Send an email/SMS
Connect the robot to a database
Access the database via a website
